'''索倫眼龍屬'''（[[学名|屬名]]：''{{lang|la|Sauroniops}}''）又稱'''索倫龍'''，是[[獸腳亞目|獸腳亞目]][[恐龍|恐龍]]的一[[屬|屬]]，為[[鯊齒龍科|鯊齒龍科]]家族的基幹成員之一，生存於約一億年前左右的[[白堊紀|白堊紀]][[森諾曼期|森諾曼期]]早期，化石發現於[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的[[拉希迪耶省|拉希迪耶省]]東部<ref name = Cau>{{cite journal | author = Cau, A.; Dalla Vecchia, F. M.; Fabbri, M. | title = A thick-skulled theropod (Dinosauria, Saurischia) from the Upper Cretaceous of Morocco with implications for carcharodontosaurid cranial evolution | journal = ''Cretaceous Research'' | volume = 40 | pages = 251–260 | year = 2012 | issn = 0195-6671 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2012.09.002 | url = https://www.academia.edu/3480131/A_thick-skulled_theropod_Dinosauria_Saurischia_from_the_Upper_Cretaceous_of_Morocco_with_implications_for_carcharodontosaurid_cranial_evolution | access-date = 2017-02-15 | archive-date = 2020-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200511223438/https://www.academia.edu/3480131/A_thick-skulled_theropod_Dinosauria_Saurischia_from_the_Upper_Cretaceous_of_Morocco_with_implications_for_carcharodontosaurid_cranial_evolution | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

部分古生物學家將索倫眼龍視為[[撒哈拉鯊齒龍|撒哈拉鯊齒龍]]的[[異名|異名]]<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Ibrahim, N.; Sereno, P.C.; Varricchio, D.J.; Martill, D.M.; Dutheil, D.B.; Unwin, D.M.; Baidder, L.; Larsson, H.C.E.; Zouhri, S.; Kaoukaya, A. | title = Geology and paleontology of the Upper Cretaceous Kem Kem Group of eastern Morocco | journal = ''ZooKeys'' | volume = 928 | pages = 1–216 | year = 2020 | issn = 1313-2989 | doi = 10.3897/zookeys.928.47517 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/340819682_Geology_and_paleontology_of_the_Upper_Cretaceous_Kem_Kem_Group_of_eastern_Morocco }}</ref>，但此論點仍有爭議<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/116384031784763/posts/2922242531198885/|title=[Brief comments to two statements in Ibrahim ''et al''. 2020]|last=Cau|first=Andrea|date=22 April 2020|website=Facebook|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511223449/https://www.facebook.com/116384031784763/posts/2922242531198885/|access-date=2020-04-24|archive-date=2020-05-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 特徵描述 ==
由於目前對索倫眼龍的認識全都只來自一批屬於上頭骨的部分化石，因此所知有限。但根據這些頭骨化石推算得知，索倫眼龍的身長可能達12公尺以上，這在鯊齒龍科家族中屬於中大型，但以[[獸腳類|獸腳類]]恐龍而言已經算是巨型。此外索倫眼龍的頭骨化石也具有數個能和其他鯊齒龍類區分開來的特徵，包括以下幾點：
* 前鼻突（nasal processes of the frontal）的背面具有橫向突出，[[鼻骨|鼻骨]]和[[額骨|額骨]]的接觸面積占了額骨（接觸表面）的40%以上。
* 前額骨和[[淚骨|淚骨]]背側表面有增厚的圓拱狀隆起。

但索倫眼龍最顯著的特徵莫過於其背外側增厚的[[額骨|額骨]]（dorsoventrally thickened frontal），科學家推測，這種加厚的結構可能是為了適應或應付頻繁的頭部撞擊，比如說雄性之間經常發生的打鬥<ref name = NatGeo>{{cite news | url = http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2012/11/121106-sauron-new-dinosaur-lord-of-the-rings-science-t-rex/ | author = James Owen | work = [[National_Geographic|National Geographic]] | title = New "Sauron" Dinosaur Found, Big as T. Rex"" | date = November 6, 2012 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | archive-date = 2018-08-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180822114854/https://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2012/11/121106-sauron-new-dinosaur-lord-of-the-rings-science-t-rex/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

